(58, 1, '2018-06-09 09:56:43', '2018-06-09 09:56:43', 'Home Decor Solutions, Inc. is located at 311 Judges Road, Unit 1- D Wilmington, N.C. We offer Free, In-home Consultations for Southeastern North Carolina, which includes Wilmington, N.C., Leland, Southport, Brunswick and Pender counties, and Carolina, Wrightsville and Kure beaches.\r\n\r\nHome Décor Solutions, Inc of Wilmington offers you a broad selection of affordable window coverings and window blinds in the most popular brand names. You can view plantation shutters from Norman, honeycomb shades from Hunter Douglas, or cellular shades and bamboo shades from Enlightened Style by Alta. We also offer our own premium brand of window blinds and window coverings - Signature Series by Budget Blinds.\r\n\r\nWe offer fabric treatments from top name brands like Lafayette, Carole Fabrics, Phase II, Kashmir and many more. Additionally, we specialize in custom draperies, valances, toppers, panels, bedspreads, table runners and more. With a full line of fabrics in the latest styles and fashions, we have what you need to complete your soft fabric treatment needs. We can even work with your own fabric if that is your desire.\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to organization, Home Décor Solutions can maximize any space, while also customizing it to your specific needs. Featuring ClosetMaid® wood-laminate and ventilated systems, we provide 3-Demensional designs so you can see your closet before you purchase, making the process worry-free, hassle-free and a superior experience.\r\n\r\nFor your exterior product needs, Home Décor Solutions carries a full line of outdoor products including Hurricane Shutters, Retractable Screens, Solar Screens, Retractable Awnings, Bermuda Shutters, and much more.\r\n\r\nHome Décor Solutions understands that your time is valuable and our goal is to make Your House, Your Home by providing many of the home accessory products at one location, saving you time and money. One Click, One Call, or One Visit to our beautiful showroom will allow you to see how our experience, knowledge and professionalism is second to none.', 'About Us', 'Home Decor Solutions, Inc. is located at 311 Judges Road, Unit 1- D Wilmington, N.C. We offer Free, In-home Consultations for Southeastern North Carolina, which includes Wilmington, N.C., Leland, Southport, Brunswick and Pender counties, and Carolina, Wrightsville and Kure beaches.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-09 09:56:43', '2018-06-09 09:56:43', '', 13, 'http://localhost/ThemeIntegration/2018/06/09/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
